summary: LETTERR FROM M TONY PRIESGEN (WI) EXPRESSING HIS  OPPOSITION TO  NEW EARLY WARNING  REPORT (EWR) REGULATIONS THAT REQUIRED OVER 500 SMALL TO MEDIUM TRAILER MANUFACTURERS (THOSE WITH A GROSS VEHICLE WEIGHT RATING, GVWR, OF UNDER 16000 POUNDS) TO SUBMIT COMPREHENSIVE EARLY WARNING REPORTS TO NHTSA. SUCH ACTION COULD PUT MR PRIESGAN AND MANY OF HIS COLLEAGUES OUT OF BUSINESS.  *JB .....*AK
